---
// Opção 3: Antes/Depois com mini-browsers
---
<section class="relative pt-32 pb-24 bg-transparent overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
    <div class="text-center lg:text-left">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-emerald-500 mb-8">
        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 animate-pulse"></span>
        <span class="font-medium">Nota Máxima no Google Pagespeed</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white mb-6 leading-tight font-['Outfit']">
        O Site Que Transforma Seus Anúncios em <span class="text-[#6366F1]">Clientes no WhatsApp</span>.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-zinc-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto lg:mx-0 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
        Nossa infraestrutura garante que nenhuma oportunidade seja perdida. Substituímos seu site lento por uma estrutura focada em uma única coisa: fazer seu telefone tocar.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center lg:justify-start justify-center gap-2 sm:gap-4 bg-zinc-900/60 border border-zinc-800 rounded-2xl py-3 px-5 max-w-xl mx-auto lg:mx-0">
        <span class="font-mono text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-400 whitespace-nowrap">5 em 10</span>
        <span class="text-sm text-zinc-300 text-center sm:text-left">clientes perdidos por sites lentos <span class="text-zinc-500">(Google)</span></span>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-10">
        <a href="#planos" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-base px-8 py-4 bg-[#6366F1] text-white font-semibold rounded-xl hover:bg-indigo-500 hover:shadow-[0_0_24px_rgba(99,102,241,0.4)] transition-all">
          Ver Planos
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none"><path d="M1 7h12M7 1l6 6-6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Direita: Antes / Depois -->
    <div class="relative w-full mt-8 lg:mt-0">
      <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-indigo-500/10 blur-[80px] rounded-full pointer-events-none"></div>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-center">
          <p class="text-xs font-mono text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest">Antes</p>
          <p class="text-xs font-mono text-[#6366F1] uppercase tracking-widest">Depois</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <!-- ANTES -->
          <div class="bg-[#111115]/80 border border-zinc-800/80 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl">
            <div class="bg-zinc-900 px-3 py-2.5 flex items-center gap-2 border-b border-zinc-800">
              <div class="flex gap-1.5">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red-500/60"></div>
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/40"></div>
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-zinc-700"></div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex-1 bg-zinc-800 rounded h-4 flex items-center px-2">
                <span class="text-[9px] text-zinc-600 truncate">seusite.com.br</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-5 h-44 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 border-2 border-zinc-700 border-t-red-400 rounded-full animate-spin"></div>
              <p class="text-xs text-zinc-600 text-center">Carregando...<br/>aguarde</p>
              <div class="text-xs text-red-400 font-mono bg-red-500/10 px-2 py-1 rounded-md">4.5s ▼</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- DEPOIS -->
          <div class="bg-[#111115]/80 border border-[#6366F1]/30 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl shadow-indigo-500/10">
            <div class="bg-zinc-900 px-3 py-2.5 flex items-center gap-2 border-b border-zinc-800">
              <div class="flex gap-1.5">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red-500/60"></div>
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/60"></div>
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/60"></div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex-1 bg-zinc-800 rounded h-4 flex items-center px-2">
                <span class="text-[9px] text-zinc-400 truncate">seusite.com.br</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-5 h-44 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-full space-y-2">
                <div class="h-2 bg-zinc-700 rounded-full w-3/4 mx-auto"></div>
                <div class="h-1.5 bg-zinc-800 rounded-full w-1/2 mx-auto"></div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-emerald-500 text-white text-xs font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-full">
                <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347z"/></svg>
                Falar no WhatsApp
              </div>
              <div class="text-xs text-emerald-400 font-mono bg-emerald-500/10 px-2 py-1 rounded-md">0.8s ✓</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[#111115]/60 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-2xl py-4 px-5 text-center">
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-300">Seu cliente chega <span class="text-white font-semibold">instantaneamente</span> no botão de contato — sem esperar, sem desistir.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
